trans-unit.source: Exposes <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> types to UI Automation.
The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" /> class.
The data item that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewDataItemAutomationPeer" />.

Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewDataItemAutomationPeer" /> for a data item in the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items" /> collection of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeView" />의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items" />컬렉션에 데이터 항목의 새 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewDataItemAutomationPeer" /> 인스턴스를 만듭니다.

trans-unit.source: A new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewDataItemAutomationPeer" /> for <paramref name="item" />.
The item to get an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ItemAutomationPeer" /> for.
Returns an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ItemAutomationPeer" /> for the specified object.
An <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.ItemAutomationPeer" /> for the specified object.
Gets the control type for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />.
This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetAutomationControlType" />.
The <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationControlType.TreeItem" /> enumeration value.

Gets the collection of child elements of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" />에 연결된 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />의 자식 요소 컬렉션을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetChildren" />.
The collection of child elements.
This method is recursive.
That is, it returns the hierarchy of child objects of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem>.
trans-unit.target: 즉, 계층의 자식 개체를 반환 된 <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />.
This method is called by <see cref="M:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.AutomationPeer.GetClassName" />.
A string that contains "TreeViewItem".
One of the enumeration values.
Gets the control pattern for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TreeViewItem" /> that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />.

If <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ScrollItem" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SelectionItem" />, or <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" />, this method returns the current instance of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />; otherwise, it returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="patternInterface" />가 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ScrollItem" />, <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.SelectionItem" /> 또는 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.ExpandCollapse" />이면 이 메서드는 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.TreeViewItemAutomationPeer" />의 현재 인스턴스를 반환하고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="null" />을 반환합니다.
